{"id":"371c7137-3b2b-4140-93b5-d1993fcb19e1","name":"Bayonetta","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">\"Oh my… That was bloody amazing.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/m/dEJJybsju8EAAAAC/bayo-bayonetta.gif\" alt=\"a woman is holding a gun in a video game while standing in front of a fountain .\" style=\"width: 833px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" width=\"833\" height=\"465.959375\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"If you need to learn how to talk to a lady, ask your mum!\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/m/1A1lf1R4pX0AAAAC/bayonetta.gif\" alt=\"a woman in a video game is holding a red object\" style=\"width: 833px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" width=\"833\" height=\"583.1\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"I have a burning desire to send you back to your maker...\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/m/D5RKGOw1OEYAAAAd/bayonetta-morning.gif\" alt=\"a close up of a person 's chest with a black jacket and red tie\" style=\"width: 833px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" width=\"833\" height=\"833\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\"><strong>Bayonetta</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">(real name </span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\"><strong>Cereza</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">) is the main protagonist of the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://bayonetta.fandom.com/wiki/Bayonetta_(series)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\"><em>Bayonetta</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\"> series</span><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58)\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> She is a coquettish and mysterious </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://bayonetta.fandom.com/wiki/Umbra_Witches\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\">Umbra Witch</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58)\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Considered the black sheep of the Umbra Witches due to her Umbran and Lumen descent, she possesses a remarkable talent for</span><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 58, 58)\"> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://bayonetta.fandom.com/wiki/Bullet_Arts\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\">Bullet Arts</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> and possessed the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://bayonetta.fandom.com/wiki/Left_Eye_of_Darkness\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 13, 13)\">Left Eye of Darkness</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/bb/e4/d6/bbe4d6637aa6ceb9218a4a14b359bd5d.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"object-fit: contain; margin: 0px auto;\" loading=\"auto\" class=\"hCL kVc L4E MIw N7A XiG\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2aa17f79-0e24-4a7c-b400-0786fd6d79c9_1f2d734d-5f87-43ef-a3d6-62c15e92cbc0.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical"],"chats":3044,"messages":48305,"created_at":"2025-02-18T17:28:09.026834+00:00"}